high_descs: Turn left and take a half step to your left then walk to the couch in front of you and turn to the right and walk until your are even with the coffee table to your right then turn right to face it.
Pick up the keys in the middle of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk to the chair then turn left and walk until you are even with the other chair to your right and then turn to face it.
Put the keys in the middle of the cushion towards the edge.
Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the circular stand with a light on it.
Pick up the keys that are behind the light.
Walk back to where you put the first set of keys.
Put these keys to the right of the other keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on a chair.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the far side of the coffee table.
Pick up the keys off of the coffee table.
Turn right and walk towards the chair, after the coffee table hang a left and start walking forwards, stop at the last chair and turn right to face it.
Place the keys on the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk over to the small black table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the keys off of the small black table.
Turn around and walk back over to the chair with the keys on its seat.
Place the keys on the seat of the chair to the right of the keys that are already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two keys to a chair seat.
